c: 57
v: 29
t: "aetakm allah taealaa dhlk klh; liaelam 'ahl alkitab aladhin lam yuminuu bmhmd salaa allah ealayh wslm, 'anahum la yaqdirun ealaa shay' min fadl allah yksbwnh lanfshm 'aw ymnhwnh lghyrhm, wa'ana alfadl klh biad allah wahdah yutih man yasha' min ebadh, wallah dhu alfadl aleazim ealaa khlqh"